• Possibilité: SQL
   ◦ Exemple pour un module:
      ```sql create table units (id integer primary key,
                          name varchar(100),
                          semester integer,
                          credit_count integer,
                          is_registrable boolean,
                          is_registered boolean,
                          flags enum('Optional','Progressive','RoadblockCycle','MultipleRegistration','Mandatory'))
      insert into units(*) values ('Nom de module', 6, 20, true, false, ('Optional'))```

